The Safari was to return to the WRC series this year after staying out in the cold since 2002, but the eagerly-awaited comeback was delayed by the coronavirus pandemicAmina projected that the WRC Safari Rally will converge in excess of 825 million visitors in the form of spectators, online games participants on Safari Play Station and global television viewershipThe CS noted that apart from competition, the WRC safari Rally will also play a leading role in propagating road safety